OL,4,Csuspension after appeal fails
OL,6,FScott Benton 'committed an extremely
OL,7,Fserious breach of the rules' when he
OL,8,Fwas caught offering to lobby ministers
OL,9,Fon behalf of gambling investors.
OL,10,FPolitical correspondent Andrew Misra
OL,11,Freports.
OL,13,FThe former MP for Blackpool South will
OL,14,Fbe suspended after his appeal against
OL,15,Fthe Standards Committee's decision was
OL,16,Fdismissed by an independent panel.
OL,18,FScott Benton will be given the 35 day
OL,19,Frecommended suspension after an
OL,20,Findependent panel dismissed his appeal.
