OL,3,CMP caught in lobbying sting faces
OL,4,Csuspension after appeal fails
OL,6,FHe appeared to suggest MPs allow
OL,7,Fcompanies to put a falsely low value
OL,8,Fon tickets they have accepted for live
OL,9,Fsports and cultural events, in order
OL,10,Fto avoid the requirement to disclose
OL,11,Fhospitality worth #300 or more.
OL,13,FThe Commons standard watchdog
OL,14,Frecommended a 35 day suspension but
OL,15,FBenton appealed the decision, saying
OL,16,Fhis actions were an "extremely serious
OL,17,Fbreach."
