OL,6,FHe claimed it was "was heavily
OL,7,Finfluenced by the memorandum submitted
OL,8,Fby the Parliamentary Commissioner for
OL,9,FStandards which makes several pivotal
OL,10,Fstatements that are completely
OL,11,Ffactually inaccurate".
