OL,6,FHe said he believed a second
OL,7,Fassessment will "consider the facts
OL,8,Fand lead to a more equitable decision".
OL,10,FThe independent panel dismissed both
OL,11,Farguments, saying there was "no
OL,12,Fsubstance" to his claims against the
OL,13,Fcommissioner and that an investigation
OL,14,Fby the Standards Committee found there
OL,15,Fhad been no leak of its decision.
OL,17,FThe panel also found there was "no
OL,18,Fsubstance" to Mr Benton's claims that
OL,19,Fthe recommended suspension was
OL,20,F"unreasonable and/or disproportionate".
