OL,6,FThe Conservatives won Blackpool South
OL,7,Fin 2019 with a majority of just 3,690,
OL,8,Fraising the prospect of another
OL,9,Fdifficult by-election for the Prime
OL,10,FMinister after losses in
OL,11,FWellingborough and Kingswood last week.
OL,13,FIt would be the fourth such vote held
OL,14,Fthis year, while a loss would be the
OL,15,F11th time the Government has lost a
OL,16,Fseat in a by-election since the start
OL,17,Fof the current parliament in 2019.
OL,19,FLabour have called on Mr Benton to
OL,20,Fresign immediately rather than wait
OL,21,Ffor the outcome of any recall petition.
