OL,6,F"How can MPs and the public they serve
OL,7,Fhave faith in standards process which
OL,8,Fdoesn't adhere to its own ethics,
OL,9,Fstandards and principles? To make
OL,10,Fmatters worse, the decision of the
OL,11,FAppeal Panel (the timing of which
OL,12,Fshould have again been unknown) was
OL,13,Fleaked to the press with journalists
OL,14,Fcontacting me last night regarding
OL,15,Fthis and the decision being leaked
OL,16,Fthis morning. Despite being aware of
OL,17,Fyet more leaks, the Appeal Panel
OL,18,Fchooses to ignore this and the obvious
OL,19,Fflaws and bias within the process
OL,20,Fwhich they so clearly demonstrate."
